highlights.text: “反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1580 days straight.
Anson Lo 盧瀚霆 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “Lemonade” is the highest at #3.
“遇見” by Stefanie Sun is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 83 spots at #112.
“5, 4, 3 (Pretty woman) (feat. Lay Bankz)” by CxM and Lay Bankz is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #49.
